      • getRate

        public double getRate(VegetativeType vegType,
             boolean isExtreme,
             Evu fromEvu,
             int tStep,
             Lifeform lifeform)
        Matches the Evu fire spreading from, the time step, lifeforms, and vegetative type returns the spread time based on whether the fire is extreme. Gets the Evu polygon side length and casts to double. If rate is greater than 0 length/rate = spreadtime. otherwise it reaturns the length.
        Parameters:
        vegType - the vegetative type
        isExtreme - boolean for fire type. true if extreme
        fromEvu - the Evu where the fire is spreading from
        tStep - time step
        lifeform - choices are trees, shrubs, herbacious, agriculture, or NA (no classification)
        Returns:
